[
	{
		"id": 0,
		"localized_name": "キューン",
		"romanized_name": "Quinn",
		"model_path_hash": "913274709521753211",
		"text": "うっ、くっ……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_200_036_00322",
		"still_path_hash": "7374237645965483172",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 1,
		"localized_name": "イェルカ",
		"romanized_name": "Jelka",
		"model_path_hash": "7989768780593008340",
		"text": "どうしたんだい？\n力ずくでも連れて帰るんじゃなかったのかい？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_153_036_00323",
		"still_path_hash": "8715905000688515801",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 2,
		"localized_name": "キューン",
		"romanized_name": "Quinn",
		"model_path_hash": "913274709521753211",
		"text": "それ、は……！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_200_036_00324",
		"still_path_hash": "7374237645965483172",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 3,
		"localized_name": "？？？",
		"romanized_name": "???",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "それだけの素養があるのに後れを取るとは。\n情けないのう！　情けないがすぎる",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_228_036_00325",
		"still_path_hash": "0",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 4,
		"localized_name": "？？？",
		"romanized_name": "???",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "潜在能力の高さをすべて出し切れない。\nまだまだ心に甘えが残っているんじゃないか？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_227_036_00326",
		"still_path_hash": "0",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 5,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "誰っ！？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_002_036_00327",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 6,
		"localized_name": "？？？",
		"romanized_name": "???",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "誰とは心外じゃな。\nうぬの姉と兄であろうが",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_228_036_00328",
		"still_path_hash": "0",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 7,
		"localized_name": "シトリン",
		"romanized_name": "Citrine",
		"model_path_hash": "6017129171503572683",
		"text": "嘘……！　いつの間に目覚めて……！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_154_036_00329",
		"still_path_hash": "924100309011770274",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 8,
		"localized_name": "？？？",
		"romanized_name": "???",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "シトリン。目覚めの気分は悪いぞ。\n兄弟の意志がバラけてるじゃないか",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_227_036_00330",
		"still_path_hash": "0",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 9,
		"localized_name": "？？？",
		"romanized_name": "???",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "聞き分けのない兄弟を\n懲らしめる必要がありそうじゃのう？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_228_036_00331",
		"still_path_hash": "0",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 10,
		"localized_name": "シトリン",
		"romanized_name": "Citrine",
		"model_path_hash": "6017129171503572683",
		"text": "うっ……や、やだなあ二人とも\nじょ、冗談がきついよ、僕は聞き分けてるほうだよ？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_154_036_00332",
		"still_path_hash": "924100309011770274",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 11,
		"localized_name": "アルビーナ",
		"romanized_name": "Alvina",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "（っ……！　シトリンがあんなに取り乱すなんて……）",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_150_036_00333",
		"still_path_hash": "8874763601186801212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 12,
		"localized_name": "アルビーナ",
		"romanized_name": "Alvina",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "（なんで……足の震えが止まらない。\n　こいつら……どんだけヤバいの！？）",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_150_036_00334",
		"still_path_hash": "8874763601186801212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 13,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "6823802507187778884",
		"text": "ヴァレリアの兄弟……ということは、\nあなたがたも九偉人……？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_001_036_00335",
		"still_path_hash": "2457375212832216718",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 14,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "そういえば、まだ眠ってる兄弟が二人いるって……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_002_036_00336",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 15,
		"localized_name": "ゼロ",
		"romanized_name": "Zero",
		"model_path_hash": "6684953388752804572",
		"text": "その通りよ。我は誰も超えられぬ九偉人最強……\nゆえにゼロ！　そう名乗っておるのじゃあ！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_228_036_00337",
		"still_path_hash": "3236890542622906589",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 16,
		"localized_name": "ヘルト",
		"romanized_name": "Held",
		"model_path_hash": "1300312624310610838",
		"text": "俺は長兄のヘルト。最初に創られた九偉人にして\n英雄的存在だ。この名が示す通りにな",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_227_036_00338",
		"still_path_hash": "8474576122523799073",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 17,
		"localized_name": "ヘルト",
		"romanized_name": "Held",
		"model_path_hash": "1300312624310610838",
		"text": "やはりキューンは末っ子だから、\n甘やかされてしまっているようだな",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_227_036_00339",
		"still_path_hash": "8474576122523799073",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 18,
		"localized_name": "ヘルト",
		"romanized_name": "Held",
		"model_path_hash": "1300312624310610838",
		"text": "長兄としてしっかり言い聞かせて、\nイェルカを連れ戻せと命じたのに……まったく",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_227_036_00340",
		"still_path_hash": "8474576122523799073",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 19,
		"localized_name": "イェルカ",
		"romanized_name": "Jelka",
		"model_path_hash": "7989768780593008340",
		"text": "キューンがらしくない強硬手段に出たのも\nヘル兄、ゼロ姉の影響ってわけかい……！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_153_036_00341",
		"still_path_hash": "8715905000688515801",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 20,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "えっと、ヘルトとゼロ……？　やめてあげなさいよ。\nキューンは戦いたくないって言ってるんだから",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_002_036_00342",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 21,
		"localized_name": "ゼロ",
		"romanized_name": "Zero",
		"model_path_hash": "6684953388752804572",
		"text": "ナナ、今はヴァレリアか……哀れな妹じゃ。\n記憶を忘れ、戦い以外に余計な力を割り振られ……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_228_036_00343",
		"still_path_hash": "3236890542622906589",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 22,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "あ、哀れまれた！？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_002_036_00344",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 23,
		"localized_name": "シトリン",
		"romanized_name": "Citrine",
		"model_path_hash": "6017129171503572683",
		"text": "説得は無駄だよ。この二人は誰の言うことも聞かない。\n危なすぎるから眠らされてたはずなんだけど……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_154_036_00345",
		"still_path_hash": "924100309011770274",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 24,
		"localized_name": "ヘルト",
		"romanized_name": "Held",
		"model_path_hash": "1300312624310610838",
		"text": "これからはお前たちの力が必要だ……\n俺らを起こしたアウグストはそう言っていたな",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_227_036_00346",
		"still_path_hash": "8474576122523799073",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 25,
		"localized_name": "ヘルト",
		"romanized_name": "Held",
		"model_path_hash": "1300312624310610838",
		"text": "どういうことかと思っていたが、理解した。\nお前らは随分とぬるい「管理」をしているようだ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_227_036_00347",
		"still_path_hash": "8474576122523799073",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 26,
		"localized_name": "ゼロ",
		"romanized_name": "Zero",
		"model_path_hash": "6684953388752804572",
		"text": "下の者を甘やかし、イェルカまでも\n「管理」を放棄して、アウグストの命令に楯を突く……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_228_036_00348",
		"still_path_hash": "3236890542622906589",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 27,
		"localized_name": "ヘルト",
		"romanized_name": "Held",
		"model_path_hash": "1300312624310610838",
		"text": "俺が目覚めたからにはそのような生ぬるい\n「管理ごっこ」は終わりだ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_227_036_00349",
		"still_path_hash": "8474576122523799073",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 28,
		"localized_name": "ヘルト",
		"romanized_name": "Held",
		"model_path_hash": "1300312624310610838",
		"text": "そこにいる極夜の錬金党の連中……\nそして俺の意に反する兄弟……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_227_036_00350",
		"still_path_hash": "8474576122523799073",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 29,
		"localized_name": "ゼロ",
		"romanized_name": "Zero",
		"model_path_hash": "6684953388752804572",
		"text": "すべて我と兄者が「管理」してやるのじゃ。\n徹底的にな！　はっはっは！！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_228_036_00351",
		"still_path_hash": "3236890542622906589",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 30,
		"localized_name": "ヘルト",
		"romanized_name": "Held",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "長き眠りから目覚めた、最初の九偉人。\n強大な力を持ち、己の好きなように振る舞う気分屋",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "8474576122523799073",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 31,
		"localized_name": "ゼロ",
		"romanized_name": "Zero",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "長き眠りから目覚めた、２番目の九偉人。\n自我が強く、戦うことが大好きな戦闘狂",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "3236890542622906589",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	}
]